Æ"I wish I had the healing words
to wrap around the quiet,
Wish I knew some magic ways,
to lighten up your night,"
by Andrew W.S. Kenny: beautiful father, fantastic friend"∑
¥Peace be with you. Love to all.
Hope for our children.
Cherished son, brother, uncle, friend.
Adventurer and actor.
At one with nature, his spirit flies free.
Wise John Glynn."π
